Hi Carlos,<br>simply you can send all object&#39;s field and rebuild new object in destination process.&nbsp; Maybe, you have to delete old object in source process. Remember that you can&#39;t send address (eg: pointers)&nbsp; because they refera in local memory. If you want to do &quot;deep copy&quot; of object, you have to send the entire structures pointed to.<br>
